{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}
<!-- PLEASE ADD CATEGORIES AT THE BOTTOM OF THIS PAGE -->
This template creates a template topper to be used with [[Template:S-start/doc|succession boxes]] for members of important families or dynasties

==Usage==

===Without parameter===
The template defaults to PAGENAME and a break if no parameter is given. In the following table, the first column contains the header and the second column shows the template call used to create it.

{{s-start}}
{{s-hou}}
| <code><nowiki>{{s-hou}}</nowiki></code>
{{s-end}}

===With parameter===
The format is <code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>s-hou|''parameter''|''parameter''|''parameter''|''parameter''|''parameter''|''parameter''|''name''}}</code>, where ''parameter'' is replaced by one of the parameter names shown in the following table.

1 = Person's family name or regnal house<br>
2 = Person's birth day<br>
3 = Person's birth year<br>
4 = Person's death day<br>
5 = Person's death year<br>
6 = Person's senior family name (if house is a part of a [[:en:Cadet branch|Cadet branch]])<br>
name = The person's name if it is not the same as the page title (this option is not required if the pagename fits the individual perfectly)

;Combinations:

{{s-start}}
{{s-hou|Royal House|birth day|birth year|death day|death year|Senior house|name=Individual's name}}
| <code><nowiki>{{s-hou|Royal House|birth day|birth year|death day|death year|Senior house|name=Individual's name}}</nowiki></code>
{{s-hou|Royal House|birth day|birth year|death day|death year|name=Individual's name}}
| <code><nowiki>{{s-hou|Royal House|birth day|birth year|death day|death year}}</nowiki></code>
{{s-hou|Royal House||birth year||death year|name=Individual's name}}
| <code><nowiki>{{s-hou|Royal House|</nowiki><noinclude>''left blank''</noinclude><nowiki>|birth year|</nowiki><noinclude>''left blank''</noinclude><nowiki>|death year}}</nowiki></code>
{{s-hou|Royal House|birth day|birth year|name=Individual's name}}
| <code><nowiki>{{s-hou|Royal House|birth day|birth year|</nowiki><noinclude>''left blank''</noinclude><nowiki>}}</nowiki></code>
{{s-hou|Royal House|||death day|death year|name=Individual's name}}
| <code><nowiki>{{s-hou|Royal House|</nowiki><noinclude>''left blank''</noinclude><nowiki>|</nowiki><noinclude>''left blank''</noinclude><nowiki>|death day|death year}}</nowiki></code>
{{s-hou|Royal house|||||Senior house|name=Individual's name}}
| <code><nowiki>{{s-hou|Royal house|</nowiki><noinclude>''left blank''</noinclude><nowiki>|</nowiki><noinclude>''left blank''</noinclude><nowiki>|</nowiki><noinclude>''left blank''</noinclude><nowiki>|</nowiki><noinclude>''left blank''</noinclude><nowiki>|Senior house|name=Individual's name}}</nowiki></code>
{{s-hou|Royal house|name=Individual's name}}
| <code><nowiki>{{s-hou|Royal house}}</nowiki></code>
{{s-end}}

This template should ALWAYS be followed with a succession list and requires the bookend templates, [[Template:s-start]] and [[Template:s-end]] or [[Template:s-ref]], to work properly.

==Example==
From the [[:en:Henry VIII of England|Henry VIII of England]] article:
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext" style="font-size:95%; width:95%; overflow:auto;">
{{s-start}}
{{s-hou | [[:en:House of Tudor|House of Tudor]]| 28 June | 1491 | 28 January | 1547 }}
{{s-reg}}
{{s-bef | before = [[:en:Henry VII of England|Henry VII]] }}
{{s-ttl | title = [[List of English monarchs|King of England]] | years = 22 April 1509 – 28 January 1547 }}
{{s-aft | after = [[:en:Edward VI of England|Edward VI]] }}
{{s-end}}
</syntaxhighlight>

{{s-start}}
